Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.75,0:01:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动手前想清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此 才会反被我利用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.22,0:01:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要中这种非常明显的陷阱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.11,0:01:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者要沉着冷静地判断
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.82,0:01:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你说 我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是看你不懂才这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.87,0:01:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.32,0:01:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的一举一动 真是漏洞百出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.41,0:02:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于让我找到破绽了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真受不了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.35,0:02:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 你这个家伙太过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是替身术
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的手里剑暴露了我的藏身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是故意露出破绽的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.27,0:02:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死 我怎么会上当呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 你在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道已经被老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助绝不会发生那种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:02:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱 小心后面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫做“沉着冷静地判断”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会再中老师设下的陷阱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么又上当了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不及格 卡卡西的结论
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 刚才怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.09,0:03:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:03:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有点过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在才察觉 似乎太晚了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的声音…是小樱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者战术的心得之二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱那家伙 很简单就上当了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻术…幻觉催眠术的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也难怪那家伙会轻易上当了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟那些家伙不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是等你抢到铃铛之后再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样直接冲过来是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是陷阱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子真不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下可没空看《亲热天堂》了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 我是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助刚才满身是血
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我亲眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 不要抛下我先去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来圆柱后面是那个样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来便当就放在石头上面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者要沉着冷静地判断
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我承认 你跟他两的确不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.79,0:06:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火遁.豪火球之术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 下忍居然会这种忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:06:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的查克拉应该还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在后面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 上面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土遁.心中斩首术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者战术心得之三
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 不能动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过在我看来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很快就能崭露头角了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就叫做打压新秀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便没有傻乎乎地去抢铃铛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要躲在这里把便当吃掉 我也就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和他之间居然差这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是死人头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 你平安无事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我 不要这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快到中午了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间紧张 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 你还想继续抢铃铛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才已经摸到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定能得手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 你果然是很厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师那么厉害 我绝对抢不到铃铛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 我就不能和佐助在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.72,0:09:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正时间也不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次就不要逞强了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:10:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界上 只有我才能杀得了那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.76,0:10:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候…我哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.67,0:10:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟在说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一个复仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要超越那个家伙才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没空在这里跟你耗着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要亲手宰了那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废话太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个肚子都饿得呱呱叫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 关于这次的演习
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你们也没有必要回忍者学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我刚刚只是昏倒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也能算及格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱情胜利了 真是太帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就表示 我们三个人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 你们三个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不必再当忍者了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到目前为止 还没有一个学生及格过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊鲁卡 我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在让那些孩子们去当忍者是不是正确
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 卡卡西的判断是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不用当忍者了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的确没有抢到铃铛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可也没必要让我们放弃做忍者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个都是没有资格做忍者的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会说你是小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.82,0:12:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把你的脚踩在佐助的头上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你们几个 是不是瞧不起忍者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们认为为什么要分组进行这个演习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个完全没有搞懂这个测验的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:12:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,判断你们是否能通过这个测验的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以从刚才起 我就想问这个问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们脑袋里装的是不是浆糊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们懂不懂三人一组的用意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三人一组又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是团队合作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们互相帮助吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是 不过现在才知道已经晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们三个一起上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定可以抢到铃铛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是铃铛只有两个 要怎么团队合作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三人拼命抢铃铛的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个人一定要忍耐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样怎么团队合作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会起内讧的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们故意安排成会起内讧的测验
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个考试的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:14:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要选拔出在这种情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能不顾自己的利益
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优先执行团队合作的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是看看你们自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本不把鸣人放在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满脑子只有不知身在何处的佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老是一个人横冲直撞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你则把他们两个当成了绊脚石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己去单打独斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务是以小组来执行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对忍者来说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卓越的个人技术的确不可或缺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 团队合作却比这个更为重要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不懂团队合作的独行侠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会让同伴陷入危机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至还会送命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举个例子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱 把鸣人杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然佐助就死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:15:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴被挟持为人质
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逼迫你做出痛苦的抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而同伴的性命也会因此难保
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们所执行的任务 都是玩命的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们来看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有无数姓名刻在这石头上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些全都是被村民称为英雄的忍者们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个 就是这个 就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就喜欢这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定也要把名字刻上去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄 英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么能这么轻易地挂掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这不是普通的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么样的英雄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快说嘛 快说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都是殉职的英雄们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殉职
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了执行任务而身亡的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是慰灵碑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有好几个朋友的名字刻在这石碑上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再给你们最后一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 下午之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抢铃铛的战斗会变得更加激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有想挑战的人才能吃便当
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是决不许给鸣人吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是他不守规矩 想吃独食的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人敢分给他吃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就淘汰掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里 我就是规则
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:16:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 伊鲁卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论结果如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.39,0:17:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不要恨卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算没吃饭 也不会怎么样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我没有任何影响
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.60,0:17:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才老师不是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.03,0:17:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正他现在也不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午我们三人一起去抢铃铛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你碍手碍脚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还伤脑筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:17:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用谢了 赶快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在减肥…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 因为我吃得比佐助少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你不用放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天晓得他什么时候出现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了吗 你应该很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道啦 知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的胆子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然敢违抗我订的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还有什么想说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因…因为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…因为…因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 不是你自己说的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他们才会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是三人小组对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们三个人一条心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 就是啊 就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三个人一条心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合格…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个是第一批
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的小鬼们只会乖乖听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者要沉着冷静地判断
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打破忍者世界的规则和铁律的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都叫他废物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不懂得重视同伴的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是更差劲的废物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是…真是太帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演习到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全体合格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第7班从明天起开始执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 我成为忍者咯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:20:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就知道会这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.48,0:21:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快帮我解开绳子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.14,0:22:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么都是这种不入流的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.38,0:22:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为有像样一点的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.00,0:22:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果居然是护送这种老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别以为我们是小鬼就瞧不起我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.01,0:23:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会借此机会好好表现的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老头子 你给我听好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将来可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有在听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.30,0:23:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要任务 向波之国出发
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.81,0:23:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你 我还会继续表现的哦
